text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Nizhnebaltachevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 142 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 6 km from Nizhnebaltachevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Ivanovka, Tatyshlinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
